OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe fine
OL,6,Fweather will continue this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. There will be sunny spells
OL,8,Fto end the day, with clear spells and
OL,9,Flight winds overnight. Some frost in
OL,10,Frural areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FSunny with patchy cloud at
OL,13,Ffirst, though it will gradually turn
OL,14,Fcloudier from the east, with isolated
OL,15,Fshowers possible. A gentle easterly
OL,16,Fbreeze will develop, feeling pleasant
OL,17,Fin any sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
