OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday will be cloudier initially,
OL,7,Fperhaps with the odd shower. Dry with
OL,8,Fsunny spells on Wednesday and
OL,9,FThursday, though a brisk wind
OL,10,Fdeveloping, making it feel cool at
OL,11,Ftimes.
